Their proposals are to strengthen the voice of bankers in the Association Council, as well as to pay more attention to new banking technologies.
A negotiating process is under way, the proposals of both parties are being studied, and an extraordinary congress of the association is being held in Sochi in mid-September within the framework of an international banking forum.
